'''Robert Alvarez''' is a current [[Wikipedia:Cartoon Network|Cartoon Network]] employee and the sheet timer for the ''[[Star Wars: Clone Wars]]'' television series.<ref name="CW1">[[Star Wars: Clone Wars Volume One|''Star Wars: Clone Wars'' Volume One]]</ref> Some of his other works as an animation crew member include [[Wikipedia:The Powerpuff Girls|''The Powerpuff Girls'']], [[Wikipedia:Dexter's Laboratory|''Dexter's Laboratory'']] (which was created by ''Clone Wars'' director [[Genndy Tartakovsky]]), [[Wikipedia:Smurfs|''The Smurfs'']] and [[Wikipedia:Johnny Bravo|''Johnny Bravo'']].

